Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Get your filthy hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,off of Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.96,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:42.02,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,So you side with the Humanoid, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri has a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She has a heart just like any human's!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:59.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:02.50,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.50,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You have me quaking in my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:09.13,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The depth of your deception boggles the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:13.42,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Professor Konishi was truly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,a sinful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:28.19,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You are the devil's own invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.69,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:40.78,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If this unit hadn't perpetrated that tragedy, if it hadn't escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.70,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,the Professor and the company would be alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:48.62,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,But this {\i1}thing{\i0}, this defective pile of scrap metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:50.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:59.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri isn't... Atri isn't defective...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.64,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You're incorrigible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:09.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.98,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Then what do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.04,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Then what do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.98,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Did you see that, my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.94,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That was a display of violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.07,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This thing, this Humanoid, hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.45,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This lowly manmade tool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.57,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,struck a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.95,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,And so the truth comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.71,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This is what I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.67,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,A robot has harmed a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:40.42,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The proof is incontrovertible! This unit is defective!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.47,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,It cannot be allowed to roam free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.81,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,Y-Yasuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.57,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:28.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Please decomission me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:38.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I strike and injure people. I'm a defective Humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have to destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Atri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I said horrible things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I ran all the way here so I could apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:14.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I was so, so terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:26.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,N-No... You have nothing to apologize for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You do have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Not a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nobody knows what the heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:59.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Heck, I can't be sure where my heart is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,or if I even have one at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Same goes for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to bottle it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Just feel your emotions as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You remember now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.59,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,She's crying...{Okay, I'll be honest. I wasn't expecting this to rattle me as much as it did.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.62,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.29,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,That's her first master's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:51.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ah, yep. That explains why you found her with your grandma's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Tear stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri was crying, and she didn't even notice it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.90,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I thought she said she couldn't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was making assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She thought Humanoids couldn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That they couldn't shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That they had no heart, and no real emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.16,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But these tear stains clinched it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She does have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:31.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's been suffering since the moment she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not wanting to do the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,doing what you know is the wrong thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's been struggling to come to terms with these impulses born from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is your arm okay? Try and move it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.77,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes, everything seems to be in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Phew, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about Yasuda anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Catherine and Ryuuji are heading to the mainland to talk to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We can't get him for hurting a Humanoid,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but he did take kids hostage and point a gun at Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.93,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:28.89,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Don't beat yourself up about it! I enjoyed the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,[traumatized robot noises]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sometimes we make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:48.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We do things we shouldn't. Say things we shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:54.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's why we're able to be happy, or sad, or angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I want to be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:02.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You can tell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The key is to keep your heart under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Control your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You can figure that out as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:26.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah! Not all humans are great at it, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You might get some flak because you're a Humanoid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but I'll be there for you every step of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,For some reason, I have this incredible urge to hug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Is this a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But that's how it goes with the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.37,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Think we should make like a tree and leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.29,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't think it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:14.96,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think their bond is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.80,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Something much deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey. Atri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.18,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Maybe she's tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:35.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, she was definitely consuming a lot more power than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.77,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,She was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:44.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I think she was reading her logs before she went to school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was reflecting on what she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,what happened to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and the memories flooded back into her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,All that happiness and sadness. All at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:09.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Opened my eyes. Owner spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:14.81,Default,Nonko,0,0,0,,I'm a busy woman. You look after my daughter for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.48,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Wow! You're the Humanoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.98,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.16,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,My name's Shiina. What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.78,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I do not have one. Call me however you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.16,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I get to name you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.20,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Uh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.58,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Ruri... Natsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.38,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Betty Beep-Boop!{I got nothin.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,"Betty Beep-Boop" is a derogatory slur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.05,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Aw, but it's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.51,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Um, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.26,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.89,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,That's a migratory bird called an "atori."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.86,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,So you can be Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.82,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What do you think? Great name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That was what she named me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:23.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,"Atri." Under my newfound name, I began to live with Shiina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.47,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.72,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You'll get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.52,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You're high-spec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.52,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,High-spec?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:45.86,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mom says you're the latest high-spec model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.78,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,She said I'm in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.87,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom always says words have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:59.37,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,So you should always say good things and never say bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:05.63,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I think you should try and say it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.01,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Go, "I'm high-spec!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.68,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.68,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:30.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama's household was almost entirely just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.20,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Aw, at least go a little easy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:39.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why are you so frightened by this particular bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.87,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Just kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:46.75,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why bother making this yourself? It would be faster to just buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:50.47,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,No, no, baking it together makes for a better memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:55.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But she seems as content as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,All is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Today is Shiina-sama's first day of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I've confirmed distinct changes in her resulting from that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.73,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What do you think, Atri? How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Excellent. But according to this photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,everyone wears the same uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:19.74,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't know how I'll be able to pick you out from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:26.00,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Then if we ever can't find each other, how about we sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.96,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Remember that song I taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:39.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.97,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.77,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.85,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,We're about the same height now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:53.99,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I guess now I'm gonna be the bigger kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:02.50,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That was the last time I saw Shiina-sama smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:12.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,According to the report filed by the school, it started with something inconsequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:18.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama reproached another girl for talking during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:22.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It is assumed that the girl in question nursed a grudge over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,She held authority within the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,and thus many people became complicit in her hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:36.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It was judged to be a case of a societal issue called "bullying."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.95,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I told you not to move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.37,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Stress levels rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Today makes three months of stress in the red zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,She is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.27,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You should talk to Nonko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.23,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,She says the sea levels are rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.15,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,and humanity's gonna be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.32,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Not that anyone in the lab believes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.99,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom's gone nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Words have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If you don't mean-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.17,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.97,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,All you have to do is sit here and twiddle your thumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.30,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What would you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:46.02,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.98,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Of course not. You're a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.23,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You don't even {\i1}have{\i0} feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Stress levels continue to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Something must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.75,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,At school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,the class chose the lead actor for its play at the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:30.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that she was chosen for the role against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.57,Default,Female student D,0,0,0,,I heard she's about to jump off the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:36.98,Default,Female Student E,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.99,Default,Female Student D,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.21,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.26,Default,Teacher B,0,0,0,,That's right, Yachigusa-san! Let's all calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.59,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,We all know you don't have the guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.64,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.01,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,If you really wanna die, why don't you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.18,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Then you won't have to be in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.73,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Go on, jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.36,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:26.41,Default,Female Student A; B and C,0,0,0,,Jump off! Jump off! Jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:21.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If she jumps, she has a 97% chance of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Danger. Danger. Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.45,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,The next thing I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.27,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.52,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:08.57,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.00,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I... I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:21.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But despite all that, Atri still loved Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She wanted to be of use to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:31.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And that's why she escaped when they took her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. And then she stayed out of sight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and watched over Mom in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:49.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:55.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Even after Mom graduated, grew up, and had me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,was always...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,always...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,always there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:10.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And I'm guessing Grandma found her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:15.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,erased her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,and put her to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:22.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um, may I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:46.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I thought it'd look a little different now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but it hasn't changed a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:52.30,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's where I was watching you from.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You were, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:23:00.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,At the time, I was contemplating shutting down in this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:03.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Just like you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:09.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I failed to save my dear Shiina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:11.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:17.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,At the time, you never once smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:24.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,So I employed the song and words Shiina-sama taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There, there. Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:32.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mom's grateful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. She was always talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:48.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,how there was someone she needed to apologize to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:53.07,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,She was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:55.74,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I loved her more than anyone in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:58.16,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,but I said some horrible things to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:00.96,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:07.21,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I hope I can see her again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:09.84,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:17.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:21.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,For the longest time, I never knew who she was talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.27,0:24:25.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but now I'm certain it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.69,0:24:31.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You were her best friend in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.61,0:24:36.57,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:39.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shiina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.50,0:24:50.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:53.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be comforted...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.97,0:24:58.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I wanted to be someone who comforts people...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:25:00.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,with these very words.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:02.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.02,0:25:05.35,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.94,0:25:08.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.27,0:25:11.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:16.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Atri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.95,0:25:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
